<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- maḥabãẗu ạlậbi samat̊
 yā rabũ man̊ yud̊rikuhā
 biạlrũwḥi qad̊ ṣārat̊ lanā
 wāản̊ta qad̊ ạảẓ̊har̊tahā

[V2]
 2- lanā ạsẖ̊tirākuⁿ maʿ̊ka fī
 ạlnũwri ạảmāma ạlậbi tām̃̊
 ḥaẙtẖu tuḍī ạảm̊jāduhu
 fī waj̊hika ʿalay̱ ạldãwām̊

[V3]
 3- fakulũ mā lilậbi lak̊
 gẖināka lạ yuq̊ṣīhi ḥad̃
 fī kulĩhi kanīsatuk̊
 lahā ạsẖ̊tirākuⁿ lilạảbad̊

[V4]
 4- wakulũ ḥubĩ ạlậbi lak̊
 ạản̊ta ạb̊nahu ạl̊ḥayã ạl̊waḥīd̊
 ạảsẖ̊rak̊ta fīhi jasadak̊
 yā lahu min̊ siriⁿ̃ majīd̊

[V5]
 5- biḥubĩka ạảʿ̊ṭaẙtanā
 ạl̊maj̊da ạlãdẖī ạk̊tasab̊tahu
 wasẖurakā ṣir̊nā kadẖā
 fī kulĩ mā ạủwritẖ̊tahu

[V6]
 6- lakin̊ bimaj̊dika ạlãdẖī
 tuʿādilu ạlậba bihi
 nas̊judu bal̊ ṭūla ạl̊maday̱
 nan̊ẓuru maj̊daka ạl̊bahī̃</lyrics>
<title>mḥbẗ ạlậb smt</title>
</song>